    "The article emphasizes the importance of leveraging ChatGPT advantages to produce content efficiently and in short times but also points out the disadvantage of a potential lack of ethical responsibility in some users' research productions.According to Atencio-González et al. [27], the research developed analyzed the use of ChatGPT to promote critical thinking in university students.",
    "The descriptive and documentary study examined how ChatGPT influences the development of critical thinking, challenging traditional teaching practices by allowing the individualization of learning.",
